There are two candidate CDs. 
 The positive CD has the following information: Ladies & Gentlemen: The Best of George Michael — close‑mic, tactile lead vocals set forward with warm midrange presence; transparent, dynamics‑preserving mastering, tasteful strings/piano and clean guitar/sax, restrained percussion, concise radio edits and tight sequencing — ideal for listeners preferring forward, detail‑preserving mixes.. 
