- Preferences: curated, close‑mic, tactile lead vocals presented warmly front‑and‑center with conversational storytelling immediacy; transparent, dynamics‑preserving mastering; restrained reverb that leaves quiet moments intact; midrange‑forward intimacy; warm yet clear midrange presence; transient detail; punchy but controlled drums; tight sequencing and concise arrangements; clear instrument separation; harmonies and supportive accompaniment that enhance rather than crowd the vocal.
