Why the Expansive double‑LP is the best fit
- Vocals: The double‑LP explicitly offers close‑miked, tactile midrange vocals pushed front‑and‑center, which directly matches my desire for upfront, present vocal delivery. That addresses my core preference for immediacy and presence.
